name: 3R-3MP Girls_Frontline
description:
Use to 1 ~ 0.8

You can create a total of 4 outfits.

She can change into different outfits by writing out the prompts!

If her hat is not generated, write a prompt 'hat'

The keywords are '(costume), twintails, (or) twin_braids,'.

If her outfit is not generating well, write additional prompts.

1.Normal

sr-3mp, twin_braids, miniskirt, navel,

2.Black Rabbit Macchiato

dress, twintails,

3.Special Attack Squad Leader Bunny

school_uniform, twin_braids, animal_ears,

or

school_uniform, twin_braids, animal_ears, swimsuit_under_clothes, shirt,

4.Shrine Maidens Super Lucky Draw

kimono, twintails,
